snippet.title: SCAD - The Savannah College of Art and Design
snippet.description:
Welcome to the official YouTube channel for the Savannah College of Art and Design! Enjoy a collection of videos celebrating on all things SCAD, including our campus locations in Atlanta and Savannah, Georgia, and Lacoste, France; our award-winning eLearning programs; as well as university news and announcements. You’ll also find interviews with special guest artists and designers, features about our accomplished students and alumni, and all-access looks at our signature events, like the SCAD Savannah Film Festival, the SCAD Fashion Show, and the SCAD Sidewalk Arts Festival. You can even see highlights from our innovative academic degree programs, including Graphic Design, Animation, Fashion, Photography, Film and Television, and Performing Arts, just to name a few.

New videos are uploaded every week, so subscribe today to see the latest films from SCAD – The University for Creative Careers!
